Class ObsAggregationPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.observability.monitoring.daemon.ObsAggregationPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ObsAggregationPlugin
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.collectd.api.CollectdConfigInterface, org.collectd.api.CollectdInitInterface, org.collectd.api.CollectdReadInterface, org.collectd.api.CollectdWriteInterface, org.collectd.api.CollectdShutdownInterface
    ObsAggregationPlugin is a Java plugin for Collectd. It performs the following functions:
    1. Receive performance data from Collectd server as a plugin
    2. Aggregate performance data according to predefined formula
    3. Send aggregated data out to be saved

    Build jar file: jar cvf obsaggregation.jar com/observability/monitoring/daemon/ObsAggregationPlugin.class
